data.description: Step into modern comfort and style with this thoughtfully updated ranch in Monitor Township! A perfect fusion of contemporary living and classic charm, this three-bedroom, single-bath home boasts not one but two showers for added convenience.  Recent renovations have elevated this ranch to new heights, with multiple electrical updates ensuring a seamless and efficient living experience. As you enter, the fresh allure of new flooring, a sophisticated paint palette, and stylish window treatments welcome you. Every detail has been meticulously chosen, from doors and handles to faucets and lighting, creating a home that exudes both functionality and style.  Security meets style with Blink Security, providing you peace of mind in the comfort of your own home. The large lot beckons children and dogs to play freely, and a quaint shed offers practical storage. Speaking of dogs, your furry friends will adore the small electric doggy door—a delightful addition to the home.  Embrace the promise of contemporary comfort with a new roof, furnace, and Central AC. This house is not just a home; it's an invitation to quality living. Seize the opportunity to make this your new haven in Monitor Township. Don't miss out—schedule a private showing and witness the seamless blend of functionality, style, and modern amenities that define your future home. FHA and VA eligible, this is a chance you won't want to let slip away.
